{"type":null,"faqId":37034,"title":"华为手环B2产品介绍？","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{font-family:宋体;}\n.td1{width:1.0465277in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;border-bottom:thin solid black;border-left:thin solid black;border-right:thin solid black;border-top:thin solid black;}\n.td2{width:4.8715277in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;border-bottom:thin solid black;border-left:thin solid black;border-right:thin solid black;border-top:thin solid black;}\n.r1{height:0.66805553in;keep-together:always;}\n.r2{keep-together:always;}\n.r3{height:0.40763888in;keep-together:always;}\n.t1{table-layout:fixed;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n</p>\n您好，1. 产品介绍：荣耀小K是一款集实时通话、精准定位、紧急求助、轨迹跟踪、运动助理为一体的智能手表产品。专为儿童设计，用于监护管理孩子，是智能手机的最佳伴侣。<br>\n2. 外观：产品发布4套孩子们最喜爱的Disney主题：冰雪奇缘、超能陆战队、白雪公主、玩具总动员。分别配不同主题颜色：<br>\n1）【粉红色】公主粉——白雪公主版本<br>\n2）【大红色】魔力红——超能陆战队版本<br>\n3）【浅蓝色】冰雪蓝——冰雪奇缘版本<br>\n4）【深蓝色】牛仔蓝——玩具总动员版本<br>\n3. 结构介绍：<br>\n开机：长按侧键3s<br>\nSOS呼叫：长按侧键5s，震动后松开<br>\n重启：长按侧键10s<br>\nSIM卡槽安装SIM时需要使用配套的螺丝刀打开卡槽，并将移动 Nano-SIM卡装入卡盖中。<br>\n<p></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2198","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750139000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":134,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"